{"tid":341163,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)生力啤生日2","createTime":"2017-07-30T14:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T17:54:42.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db470e7a99446aadc470baa140f659d1e4c513d3","tid":341163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=E5IMhoM1aM6gJ9OV%2FyPJmhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5a5b1b19\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要入V台主頁先無左上舊野...<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=E5IMhoM1aM6gJ9OV%2FyPJmhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=cc645680\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暫時解決方法睇住dailymotion或直接入V台個網睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=E5IMhoM1aM6gJ9OV%2FyPJmhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a15f4d1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://manifest.rocks/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmanifest.rocks%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F06%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=4a414a31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/movienetworkpr.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/web14.jpg?resize=1200,628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fmovienetworkpr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Fweb14.jpg%3Fresize%3D1200%2C628&h=c51eb763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.艾倫&middot;薛弗是美國特種部隊小組長，奉命率隊前往中美洲叢林執行秘密救援任務並蒐集情報。在任務完成時，他們俘虜了一名女性，隨後啟程向集合地點前進。途中遭遇不明敵人侵襲，小組成員接連被殺，僅剩艾倫與女戰俘兩人...<br />\n<br />\n2.自《魔鬼終結者》中的事件11年後的1995年，10歲的康約翰（艾德華&middot;福隆飾）與其養父母一起生活在洛杉磯，而他的親生母親莎拉&middot;康納（琳達&middot;漢密爾頓飾）則由於之前為將他培養為未來人類抵抗軍的領袖來對抗「天網」為首的機器軍團，並試圖用炸彈破壞一家電腦工廠而被捕送入精神病院，由彼得&middot;西爾伯曼（厄爾&middot;波恩）負責監管和治療。未來的「天網」這次派譴了一個新型號的終結者T-1000（勞勃&middot;派屈克飾）回到這個年代試圖終結約翰。T-1000比之前送回1984年追殺莎拉的終結者T-800更先進..<br />\n<br />\n3.雷&middot;布雷斯林（席維斯&middot;史特龍 飾）是一名技術高超的監獄設計系統安保專家，他以越獄為生，協助測試監獄的防控態度，以免犯人逃出監獄，曾在8年內從14座防衛嚴密的重刑監獄逃脫成功，並有這方面的著作出版。一次成功越獄之後，一位中情局的美女特工潔西卡（凱特瑞納&middot;巴爾夫飾）給他帶來一份新合約，讓他挑戰一個無法以合法身份存在且滴水不漏的恐怖監獄。由於有高達500萬美圓的酬勞<br />\n<br />\n4.前洛杉磯警長（阿諾飾）為逃離都市喧囂，轉調到美國邊境小鎮，卻遇上集團大毒梟逃至，企圖過境至墨西哥。阿諾和搭檔使出渾身解數、出動重火力捉拿此毒梟歸案<br />\n<br />\n8 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADB"},{"pid":"05013c40767140264dc005c4bdde55f139e2271e","tid":341163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T14:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c9bfc764604d59c15faae750c7b0e01a2a21b6","tid":341163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7c0d2f23e69aff7e81819093a1e089a04c6e24","tid":341163,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e63746e0bea8679e347